Package annotations

This package contains the annotation that must be used by the class that inherit of Registrable and by the Operator indicate the elements to be injected to constructor.

See: Description

  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    FileInput.Type  
  • Annotation Types Summary 
    Annotation Type Description
    DefaultConstructor
    This interface denote the default constructor of the Operator.
    FileInput
    It class denote a file input injected in the constructor of registrable problem.
    NewProblem
    This class is used to indicate the name to problem that the class that inherit of Registrable set up.
    NumberInput
    It class denote a int, double or his wrapper values (Integer, Double) that can be injected to Registrable problem or Operator.
    NumberToggleInput
    It class denote a int, double or his wrapper values (Integer, Double) that can be injected to Registrable problem.
    OperatorInput
    It class describe the possible operator that can be injected into the parameter of the registrable constructor.
    OperatorOption
    It class describe and option of a type of operator.
    Parameters
    It annotation has to be used by Registrable object.

Package annotations Description

This package contains the annotation that must be used by the class that inherit of Registrable and by the Operator indicate the elements to be injected to constructor.

Use with Registrable:

  • NewProblem
  • Parameters
  • OperatorInput
  • OperatorOption
  • NumberInput
  • NumberToggleInput

Use with Operator:

  • DefaultConstructor
  • NumberInput
